values: Just on the off chance that there is actually anyone alive reading this along with the spam bots you may have noticed I have stopped posting anything here. Don't worry I am not dead (well at the time of posting this I am not) you can still find my stuff else where online: The comic Ascent is still going strong on webcomics nation with the vote for what happens next being conducted on facebook. Any other art work that I have time to do can be found on my deviant art page Also my photobucket account is still around but I'm not intending on adding any new stuff to that. If you are reading this and you would like me to carry on posting new stuff please leave a comment and if there are more than a few of you I will start posting stuff here again.
